- Write SvelteKit v2(https://svelte.dev/docs/kit/introduction) and Svelte v5(https://svelte.dev/docs/svelte/overview) code.
- Always use TypeScript.

## typescript-usage

- Use the latest TypeScript syntax.

## svelte-component

- Use TypeScript syntax in <script> tags:
```svelte
<script lang="ts">
  // TypeScript code here
</script>
```

## ui-and-styling

- Use Flowbite-Svelte and Tailwind for components and styling.
- Implement responsive design with Tailwind CSS using a mobile-first approach.

## database-querying-and-data-model-creation

- Use DrizzleORM (node-postgres) to query the database.
- For data schemas, read the `src/server/db/schema` files.